GET {{baseUrl}}/Games

###############################################
# USER LOGGED GAMES
###############################################

### Get All User Logged Games
GET {{baseUrl}}/UserGames?userId=1


### Log New Game
POST {{baseUrl}}/UserGames?userId=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "gameId": 19,
    "status": "cleared"
}

### Update Logged Game (partial)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/UserGames?userId=1&gameId=2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 1,
    "gameId": 2,
    "status": "cleared"
}

